explanation: [0-0] In a room with an orange-armed leather sofa and white walls, a pregnant woman in white pajamas sits on the arm of the sofa, holding a straw fan and looking at a golden retriever in front of her. On the lower left side of the frame, there is a black commercial vehicle with an orange puppy and a little boy wearing a blue shirt and blue pants in front of the car. A wooden sign is inserted on the roof of the car, with the words "New Lantu Dreamer" written in black. On the lower right side of the frame, there is an orange tent and a woman and a man sitting on brown wooden chairs. The woman has her hair in a bun and is wearing an orange shirt and dark blue pants, while the man has short hair and is wearing a yellow shirt and blue pants.

The little boy and the puppy at the bottom run to the right, and some flower and grass patterns appear at the very bottom. The golden retriever bites the pregnant woman's clothes, and the woman protects her clothes with her left hand, then pats the golden retriever with the straw fan in her right hand. The golden retriever refuses to give up, shrinks its head, and continues to bite the pregnant woman's clothes.
